In the Matter of the Claim of Elinor Gordon, Appellant, v. Temple Beth El of Great Neck et al., Respondents. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent. Argued April 27, 1964; decided May 7, 1964. *743Leon Freedman for appellant. F. Walter Bliss for Temple Beth El of Great Neck and another, respondents.

No appearance for Workmen’s Compensation Board, respondent.

Order affirmed, without costs; no opinion.

Concur: Chief Judge Desmond and Judges Dye, Field, Van Voorhis, Burke, Scileppi and Bergan.
